         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0078.translation" corresp="#zoor0078.transcription">
            <p>Monument of Paulus, (son) of Zanneos, who died having a good name (at the age) of
                    30 years, in (the) year 292, on (the) 19th (day) of (the) month Xanthikos on
                    (the) 5th day of (the) Lord (Thursday).</p>
         </div>
      <div type="edition" subtype="transcription_segmented"><p>   <w xml:id="zoor0078-1" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>Μνημῖον</sic><corr>Μνημεῖον</corr></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-2" xml:lang="grc">Παύλου</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-3" xml:lang="grc">Ζαννέου,</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-4" xml:lang="grc">ἀποθανόντος</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-5" xml:lang="grc">μετὰ</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-6" xml:lang="grc"><unclear>κ</unclear>αλοῦ</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-7" xml:lang="grc">ὀνόματος</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-8" xml:lang="grc">ἐτῶν</w> <num xml:id="zoor0078-9" value="30" xml:lang="grc">λʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0078-10" xml:lang="grc">ἐν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-11" xml:lang="grc">ἔτους</w> <num xml:id="zoor0078-12" xml:lang="grc">σϟβʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0078-13" xml:lang="grc">μηνὸς</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-14" xml:lang="grc"><unclear>Ξ</unclear>ανθικοῦ</w> <num xml:id="zoor0078-15" xml:lang="grc">θιʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0078-16" xml:lang="grc">ἡμέρᾳ</w> <w xml:id="zoor0078-17" xml:lang="grc">Κυρίου</w> <num xml:id="zoor0078-18" xml:lang="grc">εʹ</num> </p>
</div>
